txt.en: Viznak's last plan involves collecting sticky substances from the creatures of Agarnaith and using this to climb the wall. Will his plan work?
\qSticky Stuff\q is secreted by the Huorns and slugs in Agarnaith.\n\nYou should collect \qsticky stuff.\q

'Instead of flying up there, maybe we climb up? Viznak good climber, but not that good. I can make myself better climber! Creatures in swamp make sticky stuff. Maybe I can climb high walls with it! Like a lizard! Get sticky stuff, and we try.'
Viznak can be called with the goblin-caller.\n\nYou should talk to Viznak.

'Oh yes! Super sticky!'

Viznak combines a few globs of the sticky substance and then smears it on his feet. He struggles to lift his feet off the ground and cackles with delight.

'Hahaha! Yar, pretty stuck! This will work!'
